<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 03:11:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>彭博社报道，华为、中芯国际使用美国技术制造先进芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-smic-used-us-tech-make-advanced-chips-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</link><description>据彭博社援引知情人士的话报道，中国公司华为技术有限公司和中芯国际公司将于 2023 年使用美国技术在中国生产先进芯片。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-smic-used-us-tech-make-advanced-chips-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国就业数据公布前亚洲股市创七个月新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-08/</link><description>周五，亚洲股市上涨至七个月高点，追随全球股市走势，因投资者对主要央行主导的即将到来的降息周期前景感到乐观，美元和国债收益率承压。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国海油在南海发现亿吨级油田</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气巨头中海油周五在一份声明中表示，该公司在南海发现了一个新的储量，探明储量超过 1 亿吨石油当量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 02:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国最高立法者承诺维护主权和安全利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-legislators-safeguard-sovereignty-security-interests-2024-03-08/</link><description>中国最高立法委员周五誓言要制定一系列新法律，以“实现国家安全制度和能力现代化”，维护国家主权利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-legislators-safeguard-sovereignty-security-interests-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>美元先于就业数据下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-ahead-payrolls-2024-03-08/</link><description>周五，由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔对未来几个月降息更有信心，美元迎来今年最大单周跌幅，而日元则因日本加息的猜测不断升温而上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 01:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-ahead-payrolls-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>香港政府公布新国安法草案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-government-issues-draft-new-national-security-law-2024-03-08/</link><description>香港政府周五公布了新的国家安全法草案，一些外国外交官、律师和企业正在仔细审查该文件，因为担心它可能会进一步削弱这个金融中心的自由。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 00:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-government-issues-draft-new-national-security-law-2024-03-08/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰推动和平计划，指出朝鲜参与与中国特使的会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-presses-peace-plan-points-n-korean-involvement-talks-with-chinese-envoy-2024-03-07/</link><description>乌克兰高级官员在周四与中国地区特使会面时，敦促基辅结束与俄罗斯长达两年的冲突的计划，并提交了他们所说的朝鲜向莫斯科提供武器的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 23:25:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-presses-peace-plan-points-n-korean-involvement-talks-with-chinese-envoy-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国陆军情报分析师被控向中国出售军事机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-army-intelligence-analyst-charged-with-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-03-07/</link><description>一名美国陆军情报分析员周四被捕，被指控密谋向中国出售敏感国防信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-army-intelligence-analyst-charged-with-selling-military-secrets-china-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：全球市场阳光刺破中国乌云</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>参议院民主党人敦促拜登政府提高对中国电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senate-democrats-urge-biden-administration-hike-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-07/</link><description>来自汽车制造州的三名参议院民主党人周四敦促拜登政府提高对中国电动汽车的进口关税，以应对国家安全风险，这是立法者保护美国汽车行业的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senate-democrats-urge-biden-administration-hike-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>诺和诺德预计中国今年批准减肥药Wegovy</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-expects-china-approve-wegovy-this-year-2024-03-07/</link><description>诺和诺德周四表示，预计 Wegovy 今年将获准在中国销售，并计划很快在这个最大的亚洲市场推出这款广受欢迎的减肥药，但限量发售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 16:34:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-expects-china-approve-wegovy-this-year-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>分析师表示，如果有更多刺激措施的支持，中国增长目标是可以实现的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-growth-target-achievable-if-backed-by-more-stimulus-analysts-say-2024-03-07/</link><description>分析师表示，中国本周宣布的2024年5%的经济增长目标雄心勃勃，如果有货币、财政和监管政策进一步刺激措施的支持，就可以实现。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 15:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-growth-target-achievable-if-backed-by-more-stimulus-analysts-say-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>安全负责人表示“不能排除中国干预立陶宛民意调查”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-interference-lithuania-polls-cant-be-ruled-out-says-security-chief-2024-03-07/</link><description>立陶宛反情报部门负责人周四表示，由于立陶宛支持台湾，“绝对不能排除”中国干预今年欧盟和北约成员国立陶宛的选举。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:31:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-interference-lithuania-polls-cant-be-ruled-out-says-security-chief-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院下周就 TikTok 打击法案进行投票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</link><description>美国众议院将于下周就一项立法进行快速投票，该法案将给予中国字节跳动六个月的时间从短视频应用 TikTok 剥离，否则将面临美国的禁令，此前委员会周四一致通过了该措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国新疆高级官员称伊斯兰教“中国化”“不可避免”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</link><description>新疆共产党高级官员周四表示，北京被指控侵犯人权的中国西北部穆斯林占多数的地区的伊斯兰教“中国化”是“不可避免的”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>